decl: example : f '' s ⊆ v ↔ s ⊆ f ⁻¹' v
og_raw:
example : f '' s ⊆ v ↔ s ⊆ f ⁻¹' v := by
  constructor
  · intro h x xs
    have : f x ∈ f '' s := mem_image_of_mem _ xs
    exact h this
  intro h y ymem
  rcases ymem with ⟨x, xs, fxeq⟩
  rw [← fxeq]
  apply h xs
new_raw:
example : f '' s ⊆ v ↔ s ⊆ f ⁻¹' v  := by
  rw [← image_subset_iff]

decl: example (h : Injective f) : f ⁻¹' (f '' s) ⊆ s
og_raw:
example (h : Injective f) : f ⁻¹' (f '' s) ⊆ s := by
  rintro x ⟨y, ys, fxeq⟩
  rw [← h fxeq]
  exact ys
new_raw:
example (h : Injective f) : f ⁻¹' (f '' s) ⊆ s := by
  rintro x ⟨y, ys, fxeq⟩
  rw [← h fxeq]
  exact ys

example : f '' (f ⁻¹' u) ⊆ u := by

decl: example (h : Surjective f) : u ⊆ f '' (f ⁻¹' u)
og_raw:
example (h : Surjective f) : u ⊆ f '' (f ⁻¹' u) := by
  intro y yu
  rcases h y with ⟨x, fxeq⟩
  use x
  constructor
  · show f x ∈ u
    rw [fxeq]
    exact yu
  exact fxeq
new_raw:

  rintro y ⟨x, xs, fxeq⟩
  use x, h xs
new_raw:

example (h : u ⊆ v) : f ⁻¹' u ⊆ f ⁻¹' v := by
  intro x; apply h

decl: example : f '' (s ∩ t) ⊆ f '' s ∩ f '' t
og_raw:
example : f '' (s ∩ t) ⊆ f '' s ∩ f '' t := by
  rintro y ⟨x, ⟨xs, xt⟩, rfl⟩
  constructor
  . use x, xs
  . use x, xt
new_raw:
example : f '' (s ∩ t) ⊆ f '' s ∩ f '' t  := by
  rintro y ⟨x, ⟨xs, xt⟩, rfl⟩
  exact ⟨⟨x, xs, rfl⟩, ⟨x, xt, rfl⟩⟩
